 - What do you want me to do?

63
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:54,380
Do nothing?

64
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:57,750
Should I stop seeing friends and stay in my room like you,

65
00:03:57,750 --> 00:04:01,030
