76
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:28,320
Ignore her, Hee Wan.

77
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,370
Hee Wan.

78
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:47,660
- Excuse me. 
 - You scared me.

79
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:51,400
I've been watching you from back there.

80
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,060
You look so sad.

81
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:55,780
