122
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,650
Guest?

123
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:06,790
Is that not the right word?

124
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:11,030
Well, I'm not exactly happy to see her.

125
00:08:11,030 --> 00:08:13,900
She's my so-called dad's wife.

126
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:18,150
I'm not sure what to call her.

127
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:21,830
Anyway, she...

128
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,770
