paying us so I live like I don't exist.

131
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:36,960
But I was always curious.

132
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:42,570
Why does this so-called father never come?

133
00:08:43,250 --> 00:08:45,620
Isn't he curious about me?

134
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:48,360
Do you want to see him?

135
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,710
I'm not sure.

136
00:08:56,430 --> 00:08:59,160
I don't really know how I feel either.

137
00:09:00,010 --> 00:09:03,990
I've been thinking about this since I was little,

138
00:09:06,090 --> 00:09:09,210
but I still don't know.

139
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:12,010
I'm like that too.

140
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:17,980
My mom passed away when I was four.

141
00:09:19,780 --> 00:09:21,950
The day I started elementary school,

142
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:25,330
